sequenceDiagram
    actor Comm as Client (Committee)
    participant EM as Event Manager<br/>(Create Events)
    participant CG as Calendar Generator
    participant DBConn as Database Connector
    participant DB as Database

    Comm->>EM: createEvent(eventDetails)
    activate EM
    
    EM->>EM: validateDateAndLocation(eventDetails)

    Note right of EM: Persist event data first
    EM->>DBConn: saveEvent(eventDetails)
    activate DBConn
    DBConn->>DB: execute("INSERT INTO events...")
    activate DB
    DB-->>DBConn: return result
    deactivate DB
    DBConn-->>EM: return eventID
    deactivate DBConn

    Note right of EM: As shown in architecture:<br/>"sends event details to calendar generator"
    EM->>CG: updateCalendar(eventDetails)
    activate CG
    CG->>CG: regenerateCalendarView()
    CG-->>EM: return success
    deactivate CG

    EM-->>Comm: displaySuccessMessage()
    deactivate EM
